{"title":"Fox Crossframe Pro is brand’s first peak-less helmet","link":"https://www.bikeradar.com/news/fox-crossframe-pro/","date":1697724023000,"content":"<img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-18-at-16.57.04-ce6de61.jpeg?quality=90&amp;resize=620,413\" srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-18-at-16.57.04-ce6de61.jpeg?quality=45&amp;resize=1200,799 1200w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-18-at-16.57.04-ce6de61.jpeg?quality=90&amp;resize=960,639 960w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-18-at-16.57.04-ce6de61.jpeg?quality=90&amp;resize=720,479 720w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-18-at-16.57.04-ce6de61.jpeg?quality=90&amp;resize=576,383 576w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-18-at-16.57.04-ce6de61.jpeg?quality=90&amp;resize=360,239 360w, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-18-at-16.57.04-ce6de61.jpeg?quality=90&amp;resize=180,119 180w\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Fox Crossframe Pro\" title=\"Fox Crossframe Pro\" />                                            <p>Fox, a brand synonymous with mountain biking, has launched its first helmet aimed at XC, marathon and gravel riders – the Crossframe Pro.</p>\n<p>The new launch is in recognition that growing numbers of riders, who may previously have ventured out on longer-travel rigs, are turning their attention to <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/buyers-guides/how-much-suspension-travel-do-i-need-on-my-mountain-bike/\">short-travel</a> mountain bikes and <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/buyers-guides/best-gravel-bikes/\">gravel bikes</a>.</p>\n<p><span>The Crossframe Pro is a <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/buyers-guides/best-mountain-bike-helmets-for-trail-riding/\">mountain bike helmet</a> with ventilation as a key aim. There are large vents on the side of each temple, as well as at the side and top of the head, while big exhaust vents are designed to help heat escape.</span></p>\n<div>\n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n    <img width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Fox Crossframe Pro helmet\" title=\"Fox Crossframe Side On White\" />\n\n</div><div><figcaption><span><i></i> The profile of the new Crossframe Pro.</span></figcaption><span> <i>Fox</i></span></div>\n<p>Additional brow vents are intended to pull in air and help prevent your <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/buyers-guides/best-mountain-bike-sunglasses/\">MTB glasses</a> fogging.</p>\n<p>The vents at the side of the temples are also designed as sunglasses ports, with TPU inserts in the vents to help grip the arms.</p>\n<div>\n    <i></i>\n    <div>\n  <div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure>\n<div>\n    \n            \n            \n            \n            \n            \n            \n        <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-18-at-16.57.29-9136c0a.jpeg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" width=\"556\" height=\"723\" alt=\"Fidlock buckle\" title=\"Screenshot 2023-10-18 at 16.57.29\" />\n</div>    <figcaption>\n        <div>\n    <figcaption>\n        <span>FidLock buckles are a welcome addition.</span>\n    </figcaption>\n    <span>\n                    <i>Fox</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n      </div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure>\n<div>\n    \n            \n            \n            \n            \n            \n            \n        <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-18-at-16.57.39-d104e64.jpeg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" width=\"556\" height=\"723\" alt=\"BOA helmet retention\" title=\"Screenshot 2023-10-18 at 16.57.39\" />\n</div>    <figcaption>\n        <div>\n    <figcaption>\n        <span>Fox has worked with Boa on the retention.</span>\n    </figcaption>\n    <span>\n                    <i>Fox</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n      </div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure>\n<div>\n    \n            \n            \n            \n            \n            \n            \n        <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-18-at-16.58.16-7ffac0b.jpeg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" width=\"556\" height=\"723\" alt=\"Fox Crossframe Pro vents\" title=\"Screenshot 2023-10-18 at 16.58.16\" />\n</div>    <figcaption>\n        <div>\n    <figcaption>\n        <span>Ventilation has clearly been a key design aspect.</span>\n    </figcaption>\n    <span>\n                    <i>Fox</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n      </div>\n          <div>\n        \n<figure>\n<div>\n    \n            \n            \n            \n            \n            \n            \n        <img src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2023/10/Screenshot-2023-10-18-at-16.58.25-7eccd27.jpeg?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C723\" width=\"556\" height=\"723\" alt=\"Helmet exhaust ports\" title=\"Screenshot 2023-10-18 at 16.58.25\" />\n</div>    <figcaption>\n        <div>\n    <figcaption>\n        <span>There are large exhaust ports at the rear.</span>\n    </figcaption>\n    <span>\n                    <i>Fox</i>\n            </span>\n</div>\n\n    </figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n      </div>\n      </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p>Internally, Fox says there are ventilation channels to pull warmth towards the exhaust vents.</p>\n<p>Fox has partnered with some big names in helmet tech. The Crossframe Pro is fastened with a Fidlock magnetic buckle, one that we’ve found easy to operate with one hand. There’s also a Boa fit system to ensure the helmet stays snug on your head.</p>\n<p>Safety hasn’t been overlooked either. Dual-density ‘Varizorb’ EPS foam is employed, while there’s a <a href=\"https://www.bikeradar.com/advice/buyers-guides/what-is-mips/\">MIPS</a> liner too.</p>\n<div>\n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n    \n    <img width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Fox Crossframe Pro helmet designs\" title=\"Fox Crossframe Pro Oveerview\" />\n\n</div><div><figcaption><span><i></i> Four of the six colour options.</span></figcaption><span> <i>Fox</i></span></div>\n<p>The MIPS liner is designed to reduce the severity of oblique impacts, by enabling the helmet to rotate slightly on the head before the force is passed on.</p>\n<p>The helmet comes in three sizes – small, medium and large – and is available now for £189.99 / €199.99.</p>\n<div>\n    <h5>Latest deals</h5>\n    <div></div>\n    <div></div></div>\n\n<p> </p>","author":"Tom Marvin","siteTitle":"BikeRadar","siteHash":"df99dd1320fcd97327a2def4c67247c08cd4090a7dab684a0eddb9b856f80ef1","entryHash":"3933f01a7e7f0e22291b0d01c6b735e6547b102f5d5a0256edad29f4ac13712e","category":"Cycling"}